ng your keywords list opens the doors to\u00a0new opportunities and new\u00a0potential customers. Identifying unique and well performing keywords assists all areas of your business,\u00a0including\u00a0product development and client communication. Without new keywords, you can&#8217;t grow your site traffic and find new leads and customers.<\/p>\n<p>Put simply, keyword expansion can\u00a0save you\u00a0money and\u00a0improve your business.\u00a0Benefits include:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Finding keywords with lower CPCs and higher conversion rates<\/li>\n<li>Edging out competition with words your competitor doesn&#8217;t know about<\/li>\n<li>Understanding how people talk about your product or features<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>WordStream&#8217;s\u00a0Keyword Expansion Tools<\/h2>\n<p>WordStream offers a suite of free keyword tools designed to help you continuously expand and organize your keywords for search marketing.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div data-embed-button=\"images\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:media.simple_image\" data-entity-type=\"media\" data-entity-uuid=\"fbfa240c-cb1c-48fd-9957-152273d51dda\" data-langcode=\"und\" class=\"embedded-entity align-center\">\n<article>\n<div><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/new-free-keyword-tool-cars-industry-results-17.png\" width=\"1528\" height=\"863\" alt=\"free keyword tool for paid search marketing\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" \/><\/div>\n<\/article>\n<\/div>\n<p>Benefits of using WordStream\u2019s keyword tools include:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Expand your keyword list<\/strong> \u2013 Find thousands of keywords that are relevant to your business with the <a href=\"\/keywords\/\">Free Keyword Tool.<\/a><\/li>\n<li><strong>Actionable keyword data <\/strong>&#8211; Instead of just a list of keywords, our tools give you structured, actionable data, ready to use in search marketing campaigns. For example, you can drop a list of keywords into the <a href=\"\/keyword-grouper\/\">